1062
01:52:17,636 --> 01:52:20,174
Better get on before we both freeze.

1063
01:52:30,147 --> 01:52:31,891
Here are the keys.

1064
01:52:33,651 --> 01:52:35,976
- So long, buddy.
- So long, Duane.

1065
01:52:37,029 --> 01:52:38,191
