1066
01:52:38,947 --> 01:52:40,525
I'll take care of your car.

1067
01:52:40,741 --> 01:52:43,278
See you in a year or two if I don't get shot.

1068
01:54:19,207 --> 01:54:21,496
The trucker didn't have a chance.

1069
01:54:24,421 --> 01:54:26,413
I could see it wasn't his fault.

1070
01:54:30,092 --> 01:54:31,373
The sand was blowing.

1071
01:54:31,594 --> 01:54:34,797
I never noticed him.
Figured nobody'd be in the street.

1072
01:54:35,014 --> 01:54:37,505
What was he doing out there anyway?

1073
01:54:37,725 --> 01:54:40,595
He weren't doing nothing.
He's just simple-minded.

1074
01:54:40,811 --> 01:54:42,720
- Never had sense.
- Wasn't your fault.

1075
01:54:42,938 --> 01:54:44,480
Hell, no. I can see that.

1076
01:54:44,731 --> 01:54:46,356
He was just a dumb old kid.

1077
01:54:46,608 --> 01:54:49,609
Didn't know enough to keep his ass
out of the cold.

1078
01:54:49,819 --> 01:54:51,776
Let's eat. Ain't had breakfast.

1079
01:54:51,988 --> 01:54:54,905
I'd like to know what
